---
import Headshot from "../../assets/img/jessrodier.png";
---

<!-- Main Container -->
<div
  class="mx-auto mt-20 flex max-w-6xl flex-col items-center gap-8 px-6 lg:flex-row "
>
  <!-- Image -->
  <div
    class="border-primary h-64 w-64 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-lg md:h-96 md:w-96 drop-shadow-[4px_4px_0_#7836cf]"
  >
    <img
      src={Headshot.src}
      alt="Picture of Jess Rodier"
      class="h-full w-full object-cover"
    />
  </div>

  <!-- Text -->
  <div class="flex-1 text-center text-gray-300 lg:text-left">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">
      My name is <span class="text-white text-shadow">Jess</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4">
      I was born and raised in <span class="text-primary font-semibold">Massachusetts, US</span> and graduated from <span class="text-primary font-semibold">Westfield State University</span>
      with a degree in <span class="text-primary font-semibold">Computer Information Systems and Business Management</span> in 2014. I have design and development experience in both the Ed tech
      and Climate tech industries spanning over 10 years combined.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2">
      I specialize in <span class="text-primary font-semibold">front-end development</span> using modern frameworks like
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">Angular, Astro,</span> and
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">React</span>, and have a strong foundation in
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">UI/UX design principles</span> to create engaging and user-friendly web applications that are both <span class="text-primary font-semibold">accessible</span> and <span class="text-primary font-semibold">responsive</span>.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2">
      Always eager to learn and grow, I enjoy exploring new technologies and staying up-to-date with industry trends to deliver innovative solutions.
    </p>
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-5">
      Fun Facts
    </h3>
    <p class="mt-3">
      I love coaching youth fastpitch softball, and am on the Board of Directors for both Auburn Fastpitch League and a rewarding non-profit Jax & Bash Foundation for Pets and Their People.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
